OL,4,Ccar accident says support has been
OL,5,C'amazing'
OL,7,FA family friend of a Wigtown teenager
OL,8,Fwho died from a car accident says
OL,9,F"it's amazing" the local community
OL,10,Fhave fundraised nearly #5000 for his
OL,11,Ffuneral in just under two days.
OL,13,FDavid Bark, 18, died last Saturday
OL,14,Ffollowing a road accident involving a
OL,15,Fwhite Ford Transit van on the A75 near
OL,16,Fthe village of Carsluith, on 18 April
OL,17,F2025.
