OL,5,C'amazing'
OL,7,FSean Little, who set up the
OL,8,Ffundraiser, says David would always be
OL,9,Fup for talking to people. He said:
OL,10,F"There's a Scottish saying 'boys will
OL,11,Fbe boys', that's probably a good way
OL,12,Fof describing David.
OL,14,F"Kids when they're with their friends,
OL,15,Fthey sometimes don't like to talk to
OL,16,Fyou and or say hello, but David was
OL,17,Fdifferent.
OL,19,F"If he was out with his friends and
OL,20,Fyou were walking the dog, he'd always
OL,21,Fraise his head and talk."
