OL,5,C'amazing'
OL,7,FSean says David's family are moved by
OL,8,Fthe local support they've received
OL,9,Fsince his death. He added: "People
OL,10,Fhave made 200 donations and some
OL,11,Fpeople have donated between #200 and
OL,12,F#100. Even a couple of pounds - it all
OL,13,Fadds up.
OL,15,F"We're living in a time where everyone
OL,16,Fis financially strapped up and down
OL,17,Fthe country. The fact it's totalled
OL,18,F#4000, it's amazing."
